{"tid":1508854,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"唔好個個星期日都淨係去機場會唔會好啲","createTime":"2019-08-26T15:43:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-26T18:48:03.000Z","uid":303608,"like":4,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"a7892a0ffe089c04dff2a0d710da367b3e508153","tid":1508854,"uid":303608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T15:43:47.000Z","msg":"每星期輪流會唔會好啲<br />\n機場&rarr;遊行&rarr;機場&rarr;遊行咁樣loop<br />\n<br />\n見到啲人話九月機場月 真係好驚會變返5年前一樣嘅結局<br />\n和平佔領迫政府讓步 失敗然後頹足5年<br />\n<br />\n認同機場要搞 但地區/全港性遊行都一樣需要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n831之後星期日嘅行動唔好淨係focus曬喺機場好唔好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4953dae632921263ba914e1b4a8d80e2fc8d33bc","tid":1508854,"uid":286964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T15:45:02.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: violet;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">求幫推</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">最新post 睇得清楚d + 加左明天有義士再審係頂！</span></span>(極正經)(請推至長期置頂)被捕義士進程，一個也不能少不只是口號！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1508237\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1508237</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"4e071976f3adc0a0965e4ab4950cc7dac41757a2","tid":1508854,"uid":104507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T15:45:10.000Z","msg":"會呀 機埸，商埸，地區 輪住搞<br />\n<br />\n[9月方向] 和理非行動全面升級<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1508024\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1508024</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"d209fe54487cddfc10ab5825289a0a8eaabd8e88","tid":1508854,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T15:54:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9hjf7rg.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9hjf7rg.gif&h=994c84f5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n九月一號下午一點機場見<br />\n<br />\n901機場和你塞 Channel<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https: